 realm of science fiction.\r\n\r\npaiyu camp is dug into the side of the valley, at the top of a slope under the massive flanks of the peak whose name it bears.  in order to attain a cleaner perspective on the trango &amp; cathedral group i decided to hike down to the river as close to the middle of the valley as possible.\r\n\r\nthat was entry point to the other world - the giants looming on the horizon, the clouds boiling and reforming, the small plants carving into the bed of the grinding, silty brown shigar.  i was mesmerized by the interplay of light and shadow on these iconic walls, above the snout of the mighty baltoro glacier, just ahead.\r\n\r\nmerge of 8 photographs – Canon EF-S 15 -85 mm @ 50mm/f18.  Canon EOS Rebel T1i 1/40th second exposure @ ISO 100.  Camera Raw processed &amp; profiled with Adobe Photoshop CS5/Canon IPF 16 bit print plug-in for Photoshop.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_147\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"550\"]<a href=\"http://dev.dougkofsky.com/product/welcome-to-the-baltoro/welcome_to_the_baltoro_sample/#main\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-147\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-147\" alt=\"welcome_to_the_baltoro_sample\" src=\"http://dev.dougkofsky.com/content/uploads/2013/11/welcome_to_the_baltoro_sample.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"396\" /></a> Detail View[/caption]','welcome to the baltoro','','publish','open','closed','','welcome-to-the-baltoro','','','2013-12-05 18:19:28','2013-12-05 18:19:28','',0,'http://dev.dougkofsky.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=145',18,'product','',0),(146,1,'2013-11-12 04:08:24','2013-11-12 04:08:24','','Welcome To the Baltoro','','inherit','open','open','','welcome_to_the_baltoro','','','2013-11-12 04:08:24','2013-11-12 04:08:24','',145,'http://dev.dougkofsky.com/content/uploads/2013/11/welcome_to_the_baltoro.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(147,1,'2013-11-12 04:08:40','2013-11-12 04:08:40','','welcome_to_the_baltoro_sample','','inherit','open','open','','welcome_to_the_baltoro_sample','','',