ics.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">my gear:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">canon eos rebel t1i - canon efs 15-85 mm is usm</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">canon 6d - canon ef 24-105 mm &amp; canon ef 70-200 mm t4</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">nikkor 50 mm f1.2 w canon mount adapter ring</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">schneider polarizer</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">brunton 26w solar charger</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">photoshop cs4 &amp; cs5 - ipf 6300 print plugin for photoshop</p>\r\nabout sizing\r\n\r\n<b><b> </b></b>i have unlimited editions of everything in their folio size -\r\n\r\n<b><b> </b></b>for larger blah blah limited editions\r\n\r\nif you can dream it - i might be able to print it!  feel free to inquire about custom sizing over and above the x - large size!  some of them go even bigger...\r\n\r\n</div>','The Process','','inherit','open','open','','125-revision-v1','','','2013-12-08 16:15:59','2013-12-08 16:15:59','',125,'http://dev.dougkofsky.com/125-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(494,2,'2013-12-08 16:17:05','2013-12-08 16:17:05','<p dir=\"ltr\">i have been inspired by the standards set by my heroes in their respective eras of exploration and photography.</p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://dev.dougkofsky.com/content/uploads/2013/11/frozenintime300608_450x300.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-461 alignleft\" alt=\"frozenintime300608_450x300\" src=\"http://dev.dougkofsky.com/content/uploads/2013/11/frozenintime300608_450x300.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><a title=\"vittorio sella\" href=\"http://www.panopticongallery.com/artist/vittorio_sella/#Vittorio_Sella_29.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Vittorio Sella</span></a></span>\r\n\r\nVittorio Sella came up the baltoro in 1909 with the duke of abruzzi and really introduced these mountains to the world - and he shot on 30 x 40 cm glass plates!  The abbruzzi expedition photos are magnificent and have touched the heart of many a mountaineer.  t